  "text": "There is evidence from a survey-based study of 930 Americans with MS indicating that patients wanted considerably more information about exercise and nutrition in the context of coordinated healthcare services. [CITATION_1] These data from the 930 Americans with MS align with a recent systematic review that identified the importance of on-going healthcare provider input for exercise promotion among persons with MS.",
